      "comment": "BETTORSWEETVICTORY (3) had been racing well and again performed impressively last start, making up plenty of ground but finding a couple better over 1650m at Bendigo. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Meets a similar line up and she can figure in the finish. FROSTY DROP (1) drew wide last start and was safely held, beaten 9 metres into eighth at Melton over 1720m. Starts from a far better position this time and is good enough to take out a race like this. BLAZIN HEAVEN NZ (8) is in the mix at her first run since finishing runner-up over 2080m at this track ten weeks ago. JUST PEDRO (6) has each-way claims if he can recapture the form from two starts back that saw him score over 2080m at this track.",
